OL,5,CWomen's Aid
OL,7,FA woman who found safety through Leeds
OL,8,FWomen's Aid 30 years ago now works for
OL,9,Fthe charity to help others.
OL,11,FLeeds Women's Aid (LWA) is an
OL,12,Findependent charity, formed in 1972,
OL,13,Fproviding a range of support services
OL,14,Ffor vulnerable women and families who
OL,15,Fare victims and survivors of domestic
OL,16,Fabuse, forced marriage, trafficking,
OL,17,Fstalking, and harassment.
OL,19,FThis year LWA supported 77 women and
OL,20,F113 children within emergency refuge
OL,21,Faccommodation.
