OL,5,CWomen's Aid
OL,7,FClare walked through the doors at LWA
OL,8,Fover 30 years ago. She was with her 10-
OL,9,Fmonth-old daughter looking for safety
OL,10,Fand a fresh start. Now she's working
OL,11,Ffor the refuge to help others -
OL,12,Fsomething she says is a "full-circle
OL,13,Fmoment that fills (her) with purpose
OL,14,Fevery single day".
OL,16,FShe said: "I was living in Sheffield
OL,17,Fwith my partner then and my daughter,
OL,18,Fbut he had substance misuse issues
OL,19,Fwhich impacted us, especially
OL,20,Ffinancially.
