OL,7,FHolding Warmth recipe book
OL,9,FLWA has released a recipe book
OL,10,F'Holding Warmth' created by women who
OL,11,Fhave fled domestic abuse.
OL,13,FIt hopes to show how food can bring
OL,14,Fcomfort, warmth and connection during
OL,15,Fdifficult times. Each recipe is
OL,16,Faccompanied by a personal anecdote or
OL,17,Fmemory about what the dish means to
OL,18,Fits contributor.
