OL,5,CWomen's Aid
OL,7,FNik Peasgood, Chief Executive of LWA,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our refuge accommodation is
OL,9,Fhome to a remarkable wealth of
OL,10,Fcultures, knowledge, and lived
OL,11,Fexperience, and this project has
OL,12,Fbrought the women together to
OL,13,Fhighlight the power of sharing food.
OL,15,F"With one in four women experiencing
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse at some point in their
OL,17,Flives, we hope the book offers readers
OL,18,Fa sense of hope and resilience, that
OL,19,Fit is possible to begin again and
OL,20,Frebuild your life."
