OL,5,CWomen's Aid
OL,7,FA refuge resident and contributor,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Being part of this project has
OL,9,Fmeant so much to me. My children and I
OL,10,Fare currently in a refuge, and while
OL,11,Fit's been a hard journey after
OL,12,Fexperiencing domestic abuse, we're
OL,13,Ffinally starting to heal. Our voices
OL,14,Fare being heard and through this
OL,15,Frecipe, I share not just comfort, but
OL,16,Fthe courage it took to begin again.
OL,18,F"I'm proud to share a meal that brings
OL,19,Fwarmth and connection to our family,
OL,20,Fand to be part of something that
OL,21,Fraises awareness and hope for others."
